content:
Excellent interview with our friend, Dr. Mark Bailey.

https://odysee.com/@MaajidNawaz:d/38RadicalFull:f

"They say they don’t know for certain but by analogy. Virologists also admit they have never seen a virus in any body fluid. They assume “it” is there. Real scientific, right?…

Here is an excerpt from a discussion with a current practicing virologist admitting no “virus” has ever been found in body fluid.
Sophia -What is in sputum?
Pedro the Virologist – “A lot of different contaminants, which is why you culture it. That is exactly why you culture it.”
Sophia -How do you know there is a virus in there?
Pedro the Virologist – “MOST LIKELY there is (a virus in the sputum) because…”
Sophia -Wait, you have never seen it in the sputum?
Pedro the Virologist – “You haven’t, you haven’t.”
Sophia -You have never seen it from any fluid of the human body, correct?
Pedro the Virologist - “No, maybe not, maybe not which is why you culture it.”
“Yes we haven’t actually isolated the amount of particles necessary in a sputum sample to know the virus is there, so we take that…” (he gets cut off)
Sophia - See how you are presuming right there that there is a virus. My point is if we have never taken a particle from the sputum of somebody, from urine, from blood, whatever, anything, we have nothing to talk about. (conversation ends)
Claudio Bernardo - "When we encounter a fact that contradicts a prevailing theory, we must accept the fact and abandon the theory, even when the theory is backed by big names and is generally accepted."
Game - set - match for any proof of pathogenic viruses. If they are not in any bodily fluids, then how could they then spread? They can’t... They don’t even know how they would enter a cell; but these virologists overlook these facts; and want to go to their own lab created process in which they claim that despite a virus not showing up in the fluids of the body they claim they can show up in a petri dish as a result of their test processes. Who in their right mind thinks something happening in a petri dish would prove that is what actually happens in a human."

⚗ Chemical facts for discussion:  The measured half life degradation of phosgene into carbon dioxide and hydrochloric acid in water vapor/aqueous solution (water) is 0.026 seconds (while mostly insoluble, OSHA allows workplace air exposure up to 0.1 ppmv per SDS sheets)

When fires combust volatiles, they produce carbon dioxide and water vapor.  The atmosphere is also 12%- 18% water vapor depending on humidity.  There was a lot of water vapor to help degrade phosgene in the atmosphere near the release site.

When vinyl chloride burns the mass ratio of hydrochloric acid to phosgene formed is over 575 : 1, with the next lower byproduct being carbon monoxide.

The published papers on vinyl chloride combustion indicates fish and animals likely died from acidified rain/air/water from hydrochloric acid formed by combustion of vinyl chloride, not phosgene or dioxin...

Vinyl chloride also burns at temperatures greater than 900 degrees which are sufficient to degrade any dioxide impurities in the solution by incineration (optimum temp is 1000 deg)  

Not to justify anyone's actions or seriousness of East Palenstine, but in the light of known basic chemistry, it is good to remember the knowledge of the past to help us understand better what we are dealing with...

#MakeZelenskytostartnegotiations. 😡

content:
Zerstörter russischer Panzer >zielt auf Botschaft in Berlin<

In Berlin wird in einer Kunstinstallation ein in der Ukraine zerstörter russischer T-72-Panzer vor die Botschaft des Landes gestellt. Der Bezirk Mitte erteilt der Aktion erst keine Genehmigung, der Initiator nennt die Gründe "bizarr" - und zieht erfolgreich vor Gericht.

https://www.n-tv.de/politik/Zerstoerter-russischer-Panzer-zielt-auf-Botschaft-in-Berlin-article23941207.html

Destroyed Russian tank >targeted at embassy in Berlin<

In Berlin, a Russian T-72 tank destroyed in Ukraine is placed in front of the country's embassy in an art installation. The district of Mitte does not give permission for the action at first, the initiator calls the reasons "bizarre" - and successfully moves to court.

content:
Italian planes for Kyiv

According to [La Repubblica](https://www.repubblica.it/esteri/2023/02/19/news/ucraina_italia_meloni_aerei-388637625/?ref=RHLF-BG-I388628166-P2-S2-T1) , Rome can supply Ukraine with five combat aircraft. However, the publication claims that Rome does not want to be the first in the list of "contributors" for reasons of political expediency. The Italians want to give the impression that they are almost forced to follow a long wave of allies, led by Britain, which is pushing the partners to a new decisive step. Italian Prime Minister Giorgia Meloni said that the country would decide to send them only together with other countries.

Recall that earlier Kyiv requested 200 modern Western aircraft to establish parity in the air. However, in response to this, Italy is talking about providing several seriously outdated aircraft that will not be able to turn the tide in the air. We are talking about the Tornado fighter-bombers and the little-known AMX light attack aircraft, which do little to satisfy the demands of the Ukrainian authorities, since the first is too old, and the second was not conceived for air superiority. Moreover, according to the Italian media, AMX was planned to be completely written off by the end of the year.

The help that Rome wants to provide to Kyiv looks like a mockery or an attempt under a good pretext to cheaply dispose of unnecessary and old equipment. At the same time, negotiations on the transfer of aviation to Ukraine from the West can be considered a new escalation of the conflict.  Whichever country is the first, it will remove the taboo on such deliveries, as with all previous equipment. This means that we once again see how Western states are not interested in peace, they are still interested in fighting to the last Ukrainian.

Join us: https://t.me/soroka_belaya_en !
